Package arcade.potts.env.location

Class PottsLocationContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.potts.env.location.PottsLocationContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LocationContainer
    public final class PottsLocationContainer
extends java.lang.Object
implements LocationContainer
    Implementation of LocationContainer for PottsLocation objects.

    The container can be instantiated for locations with or without regions. The voxels available in a container are not necessarily all used when instantiating a Location instance. Instead, the number of voxels is selected based on the associated PottsCellContainer and PottsLocationFactory instance.
